<h3 class='post-title'>
<a href='http://www.informationdissemination.net/2010/01/qdr-available.html'>QDR Available</a>
</h3>
<div class='post-header-line-1'></div>
<div class='post-body'>
<p>Andrew Exum has <a href="http://www.cnas.org/blogs/abumuqawama/2010/01/here-it-real-deal-holyfield-qdr.html">posted the 2010 QDR. </a> I assume that everyone already knows this, and is too busy reading the document to post here.<br /><br />In a related story, my daughter makes clear her position on the appropriate allocation of scarce defense resources:<br /><br /><a onblur="try {parent.deselectBloggerImageGracefully();} catch(e) {}" href="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_FJIwg2jbUP4/S2TLEWtshII/AAAAAAAABIE/Y41ubqldnHM/s1600-h/elisha.jpg"><img style="margin: 0px auto 10px; display: block; text-align: center; cursor: pointer; width: 300px; height: 400px;" src="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/_FJIwg2jbUP4/S2TLEWtshII/AAAAAAAABIE/Y41ubqldnHM/s400/elisha.jpg" alt="" id="BLOGGER_PHOTO_ID_5432690326192817282" border="0" /></a></p>
