<h3 class='post-title'>
<a href='http://www.informationdissemination.net/2010/01/public-diplomacy-from-haiti-wears.html'>Public Diplomacy From Haiti Wears Combat Boots</a>
</h3>
<div class='post-header-line-1'></div>
<div class='post-body'>
<p>My latest <a href="http://blog.usni.org/2010/01/19/haiti-update-tuesday-jan-19th/">article over at the United States Naval Institute blog</a>.</p>
